  <h1 class="hostile-sink-reset">Lists Sizes Sink</h1>

  <div class="spirit-container">
    <div class="spirit-container__inner spirit-container__inner--large">
        <p class="hostile-sink-reset">Breakpoint used to for sizing changes matches the breakpoint used with the Sprit Headline Mixins ( i.e. spirit-h3 ): $spirit-breakpoint-l or 1024px.</p>

        <h2 class="hostile-sink-reset">12 col ( col-md-12 )</h2>
        <h3 class="hostile-sink-reset">List Extra Large ( Default - SHOULD THIS BE NORMAL / MEDIUM? )</h3>

